# HeirClear — Pilot Product Implementation Plan

Build a MERN (MongoDB, Express, React, Node) inheritance claim tracking system. A user submits a claim → system tracks it → user sees status at every stage. Admin reviews and updates claims.

## Design Decisions

- **Admin seeding**: First admin created via a seed script (`npm run seed`)
- **File storage**: Local disk `server/uploads/` with Multer
- **Document preview**: `<img>` for images, `<iframe>` for PDFs
- **Account masking**: Show last 4 digits only (`XXXX-XXXX-1234`)
- **Signup fields**: Name, Email, Password
- **Delete behavior**: Hard delete (claim removed entirely)
- **Multiple claims**: Allowed per account number

> [!IMPORTANT]
> State transitions are enforced server-side: `Submitted → Under Review`, `Under Review → Approved/Rejected`, `Rejected → Under Review`. Any invalid transition returns a 400 error.

## Proposed Changes

### Project Root

#### [NEW] [package.json](file:///d:/heirclear/package.json)
Root package.json with concurrent dev script to run both server and client.

---

### Backend (`server/`)

#### [NEW] [server.js](file:///d:/heirclear/server/server.js)
Express entry point. MongoDB connection via Mongoose. CORS config. Static file serving for uploads. Error handling middleware.

#### [NEW] [.env](file:///d:/heirclear/server/.env)
Environment variables: `MONGO_URI`, `JWT_SECRET`, `PORT`.

#### [NEW] [User.js](file:///d:/heirclear/server/models/User.js)
Mongoose schema: `name`, `email` (unique), `password` (bcrypt hashed), `role` (enum: user/admin), `createdAt`.

#### [NEW] [Claim.js](file:///d:/heirclear/server/models/Claim.js)
Mongoose schema: `userId` (ref), `accountNumber`, `status` (enum: Submitted/Under Review/Approved/Rejected), `documents` object (deathCertificate, idProof, relationshipProof — file paths), `remarks`, `submittedAt`, `updatedAt`, `actionTimestamp`.

#### [NEW] [auth.js](file:///d:/heirclear/server/routes/auth.js)
`POST /api/auth/register` — validate, hash password, create user, return JWT.  
`POST /api/auth/login` — validate credentials, return JWT.  
`GET /api/auth/me` — return current user info.

#### [NEW] [claims.js](file:///d:/heirclear/server/routes/claims.js)
`POST /api/claims` — submit claim with file uploads (Multer).  
`GET /api/claims` — list user's own claims.  
`GET /api/claims/:id` — single claim details (own claims only).

#### [NEW] [admin.js](file:///d:/heirclear/server/routes/admin.js)
`GET /api/admin/claims` — all claims with user info.  
`GET /api/admin/claims/:id` — single claim with full details.  
`PUT /api/admin/claims/:id` — update status + remarks (validates transitions).  
`DELETE /api/admin/claims/:id` — delete claim.

#### [NEW] [auth.js](file:///d:/heirclear/server/middleware/auth.js)
JWT verification middleware and admin role check middleware.

#### [NEW] [upload.js](file:///d:/heirclear/server/middleware/upload.js)
Multer config: destination `uploads/`, 5MB limit, filter PDF/JPG/PNG only.

#### [NEW] [seed.js](file:///d:/heirclear/server/seed.js)
Script to create default admin: `admin@heirclear.com` / `admin123`.

---

