#### [NEW] React + Vite project
Initialized with `npx create-vite@latest ./ --template react`. Key files:

#### [NEW] [AuthContext.jsx](file:///d:/heirclear/client/src/context/AuthContext.jsx)
React context for JWT auth state, login/logout/register functions, and role-based access.

#### [NEW] [ProtectedRoute.jsx](file:///d:/heirclear/client/src/components/ProtectedRoute.jsx)
Route guard checking auth + optional role requirement. Redirects to login if not authenticated.

#### [NEW] [Login.jsx](file:///d:/heirclear/client/src/pages/Login.jsx)
**Screen 1** — Email + password login form, error messages, link to register.

#### [NEW] [Register.jsx](file:///d:/heirclear/client/src/pages/Register.jsx)
**Screen 1** — Name + email + password signup form, error messages, link to login.

#### [NEW] [UserDashboard.jsx](file:///d:/heirclear/client/src/pages/UserDashboard.jsx)
