#### [NEW] [SubmitClaim.jsx](file:///d:/heirclear/client/src/pages/SubmitClaim.jsx)
**Screen 3** — Account number input, 3 file uploads (death cert, ID, relationship), file validation (type + size), submit disabled until all provided, cancel button.

#### [NEW] [ClaimDetails.jsx](file:///d:/heirclear/client/src/pages/ClaimDetails.jsx)
**Screen 4** — Claim ID, date, status badge, remarks, document previews, back button.

#### [NEW] [AdminDashboard.jsx](file:///d:/heirclear/client/src/pages/AdminDashboard.jsx)
**Screen 5** — Table of all claims: user name, account number, date, status, "View Claim" link.

#### [NEW] [AdminClaimReview.jsx](file:///d:/heirclear/client/src/pages/AdminClaimReview.jsx)
**Screen 6** — Document previews, status dropdown (valid transitions only), remarks input, save with confirmation popup, action timestamp display.

#### [NEW] [index.css](file:///d:/heirclear/client/src/index.css)
Design system: professional banking theme with deep navy (#1a1a2e), gold accents (#d4a843), clean typography (Inter font), status color coding, responsive layout.

